  "dataSourceInstructions": "Primary Source (Recommendations):\r\n- Use dbo.product_affinity_topk_named (already includes product names; no joins required).\r\n\r\nFallback (only if the view has no rows for the anchor):\r\n- Use dbo.fact_product_affinity with pair_cnt ≥ 5\r\n- Return Top-10 ordered by lift DESC, confidence_lhs_to_rhs DESC, pair_cnt DESC\r\n\r\nImportant:\r\n- Do NOT join to Bronze_Ingest.products for recommendations (names are already present in dbo.product_affinity_topk_named).",
  "displayName": "Gold_Consume",
  "type": "lakehouse_tables",
  "userDescription": "Gold_consume.fact_product_affinity_topk_named\r\nPurpose: Precomputed Top‑K “frequently bought together” associations for fast recommendations.\r\nColumns:\r\n\r\nlhs_item_id STRING\r\nlhs_name STRING\r\nrhs_item_id STRING\r\nrhs_name STRING\r\npair_cnt BIGINT\r\nsupport_pair DOUBLE\r\nconfidence_lhs_to_rhs DOUBLE\r\nlift DOUBLE\r\nrefreshed_at TIMESTAMP\r\n\r\nGold_consume.fact_product_affinity\r\nPurpose: Full association table (used as fallback when Top‑K has no coverage).\r\nColumns:\r\n\r\nlhs_item_id STRING\r\nrhs_item_id STRING\r\npair_cnt BIGINT\r\nsupport_lhs DOUBLE\r\nsupport_rhs DOUBLE\r\nsupport_pair DOUBLE\r\nconfidence_lhs_to_rhs DOUBLE\r\nlift DOUBLE",
